data.title: Category:Charlotte Georgine of Mecklenburg
data.text:
Duchess Charlotte Georgine Luise Friederike of Mecklenburg-Strelitz (German: Charlotte Georgine Luise Friederike, Herzogin zu Mecklenburg-Strelitz) (born 17 November 1769 in Hanover, Electorate of Brunswick-Lüneburg; died 14 May 1818 in Hildburghausen, Duchy of Saxe-Hildburghausen) was a member of the House of Mecklenburg-Strelitz and a Duchess of Mecklenburg-Strelitz by birth and a member of the House of Saxe-Hildburghausen and Duchess consort of Saxe-Hildburghausen through her marriage to en:Frederick, Duke of Saxe-Hildburghausen (later Duke of Saxe-Altenburg).
